dataIdInfo.idPurp: This layer provides an index map that can be used to locate individual scanned map sheets.
dataIdInfo.idAbs: • This polygon shapefile is an index to 1:10,000 scale maps of Shimonoseki-shi (Japan), titled 'Ichimanbun no ichi chikeizu Shimonoseki Yōsai kinbō -- 一万分一地形圖下關要塞近傍/Ichimanbun no ichi chikeizu Shimonoseki Yōsai kinbō.’ To create this index, footprints were generated using the fishnet tool, and metadata were supplied for the digitized paper maps by Stanford University Libraries. After the footprints were created, the shapefile was trimmed and labeled according to the sources.
dataIdInfo.idCredit: Stanford University Libraries, Stanford Geospatial Center
